author: news@courierpublicationsllc.com (Staff)
title: Sunday Jazz with By the Bay
text:
Sunday Jazz with By the Bay Oct 16, 2015 By the Bay Jazz Trio returns to The Highlands in Thomaston Sunday afternoon, Oct. 25. 
Thomaston — By the Bay Jazz Trio will perform Sunday, Oct. 25, from 1 to 3 p.m. at The Highlands Coffee House, 189 Main St./Route 1. 
The trio plays arrangements of jazz classics by many composers from the Golden Age of American Song, as well as numerous Latin rhythm standards. The trio comprises Dennis Gurgul of Tenants Harbor on percussion; Shaun Bolduc from Pittston on bass; and Dick White of Warren on guitar. 
Courier Publications’ A&E Editor Dagney C. Ernest can be reached at (207) 594-4401, ext. 115; or dernest@courierpublicationsllc.com.
